comments: Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of DeRozan (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of White (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
White (SAS) places a resting hand to Murray's (DEN) back during his driving shot attempt but the contact is tactile and he does not apply any force.
RLB shows Forbes (SAS) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm after he secures the rebound.
The Nuggets inbound the ball within the legally allowed five seconds.
White (SAS) briefly places a hand around Jokic's (DEN) waist when he engages on the pick.
Jokic (DEN) dislodges Forbes (SAS) as he disengages from the screen.
Forbes (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Jokic (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LAR and LLB show Murray (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position on White (SAS) during the drive and cleanly dislodges the ball.
After the clean steal, Harris (DEN) makes incidental contact to White (SAS) as they go to the floor to retrieve the loose ball.
Murray (DEN) does not deliver any contact to White (SAS) when he slips and falls on the play.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of White (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
RAR shows Aldridge (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Jokic (DEN) during the drive and the ball is cleanly dislodged by Gay (SAS).
[Observable in enhanced video] Jokic (DEN) slides his pivot foot.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position on DeRozan (SAS) at the end of the drive.
Harris (DEN) briefly places an arm around Aldridge (SAS) when he engages on the pick but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
DeRozan (SAS) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Murray (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by White (SAS).
[Observable in enhanced video] Aldridge (SAS) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
LLB shows DeRozan (SAS) and Harris (DEN) make marginal contact when they engage and separate during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Aldridge (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Millsap (DEN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of White (SAS) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Jokic (DEN) commits a take foul on Aldridge (SAS).
Jokic (DEN) gives the necessary one step of distance on his legal back screen when he absorbs the contact from White (SAS).
LAR shows White (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Murray (DEN) and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Murray (DEN) commits a take foul on White (SAS).
Jokic (DEN) has one foot out of bounds and one foot in the air when he legally throws the ball inbounds.
